calculatorArn.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the Route calculator resource. Use the ARN when you specify a resource across AWS.

calculatorName.description: The name of the route calculator resource.

createTime.description: The timestamp for when the route calculator resource was created in ISO 8601 format.

dataSource.description:
Specifies the data provider of traffic and road network data.

The following arguments are optional:

description.description: The optional description for the route calculator resource.

tags.description: Key-value tags for the route calculator. If configured with a provider `default_tags` configuration block present, tags with matching keys will overwrite those defined at the provider-level.

tagsAll.description: A map of tags assigned to the resource, including those inherited from the provider `default_tags` configuration block.

updateTime.description: The timestamp for when the route calculator resource was last update in ISO 8601.
